  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.662,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "- Right, but I... -Thanks though, that was cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.501,
    "text": "I made it for you, so."
  },
  {
